使用说明：

1、 V1版模型使用chilloutmix_NiPrunedFp32Fix底模制作，暂未在其他底模中测试；

2、 模型权重建议设置为 0.8 - 0.9；

3、 在关键词中添加 “mole” 来还原人物脸部的美人痣；

4、 V1版模型在生成全身照方面能力不足；

5、 欢迎大家把使用过程中遇到的问题写在评论区，帮助作者进一步完善

Disclaimer:

1. Commercial use of this Lora model is strictly forbidden;

2. The relevant legal consequences arising from the use of this Lora model to create, convert, publish and disseminate relevant contents shall be borne by the model user, not the model developer.

Instructions:

1. The V1 version of this model is developed using “chilloutmix_NiPrunedFp32Fix” base model, and has not been tested on other base model yet;

2. The model weight is recommended to be set between 0.8-0.9;

3. Add "mole" to the prompts to restore the mole on the character's face;

4. The V1 version of this model is not well capable of generating full-body images;

5. Please leave your comments below to help the author improve the model.
